snippet.title: WillysGarageNorway
snippet.description:
I make videos of different DIY projects. Everything from fixing cars to programming Arduino boards.
I have made my own DIY CNC machine that I enjoy making things on. I consider myself a maker (of all things) :)

If you have any business requests or want to send me something , please contact me on:
wgn@willysgaragenorway.no
